# Summary
This documentation page describes the AppsFlyer (Cohort) destination integration in Amplitude, which allows users to send Amplitude cohorts to AppsFlyer Audiences for personalized marketing initiatives. The setup requires obtaining an AppsFlyer App ID and API token, configuring a separate destination for each app platform, and mapping user identifiers before syncing cohorts.

